text:
The Jamison family of Eufaula, Oklahoma, United States. The family: Bobby, his wife Sherilynn, and daughter Madyson, mysteriously disappeared on October 8, 2009, while their dog survived.
The family was reportedly considering the buying a forty-acre plot of land near Red Oak, about thirty miles from Eufaula, at the time of their disappearance. Their suspected remains were found in November 2013, and were positively identified by the Oklahoma medical examiner on July 3, 2014.
No cause of death was determined, and the circumstances surrounding their disappearance remain unanswered.
